  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cmain\u003e\u003carticle aria-label=\"Paper Plane Cocktail\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Paper Plane cocktail recipe is a great bourbon drink to add to your home bar skillset. If you love to order fancy and unique cocktails, this recipe is a must for you. The combination of bourbon, Aperol, amaro and lemon juice is a bright orange cocktail that is citrusy, botanical and warming with the perfect sweet and bitter balance.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eRelated: \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/old-fashioned-cocktail/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eOld Fashioned Cocktail\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/classic-manhattan-cocktail/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eManhattan\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/classic-negroni/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eNegroni\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/rusty-nail-cocktail/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eRusty Nail\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/easy-espresso-martini/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eEspresso Martini\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/bees-knees-cocktail/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eBee’s Knees\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/boulevardier-cocktail/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eBoulevardier\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/aviation-cocktail/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eAviation\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/spaghett/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eSpaghett\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/last-word-cocktail/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eThe Last Word\u003c/a\