autifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail--819x1024.jpg 819w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail--768x960.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail--80x100.jpg 80w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail--48x60.jpg 48w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail--750x938.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail--730x913.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail--700x875.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail--550x688.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail--156x195.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-ingredients-in-a-paper-plane\"\u003eIngredients in a Paper Plane \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBourbon\u003c/strong\u003e – Adds sweetness and warmth to this recipe. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAperol\u003c/strong\u003e – A citrusy, botanical liqueur that gives this recipe color and flavor. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAmaro Nonino\u003c/strong\u003e – This sweet liqueur adds unique flavor and depth. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLemon Juice\u003c/strong\u003e – Fresh citrus for the perfect balance. \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe best glassware choice for this cocktail is a \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/4aI0Zh3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\"\u003ecoupe glass\u003c/a\u003e. I used a \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/4aQWmRC\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\"\u003egold cocktail pick\u003c/a\u003e to secure my tiny paper airplane garnish.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/paper-plane-cocktail/?tp_image_id=121681\" data-pin-title=\"paper plane cocktail\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-500x500.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%201200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-ingredients.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-instructions\"\u003eInstructions \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn a cocktail shaker half filled with ice cubes, pour in bourbon, Aperol and Amaro Nonino. Then add freshly squeezed lemon juice. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eShake for 10-15 seconds until well chilled. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003ePour into a chilled coupe glass. Garnish with a tiny paper plane or an orange twist.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"960\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/paper-plane-cocktail/?tp_image_id=121682\" data-pin-title=\"paper plane cocktail\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-156x125.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%20960\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make-156x125.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-how-to-make.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-what-does-a-paper-plane-drink-taste-like\"\u003eWhat does a Paper Plane drink taste like? \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis is a sweet and strong cocktail. Composed of equal parts bourbon, Aperol, amero and lemon juice, this drink is balanced. It’s both bitter and sweet. The top flavor is citrus, followed by notes of botanical bitters and woodsy bourbon. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe Paper Plane is a modern take on the Last Word Cocktail, which is another equal parts drink made using gin, green chartreuse, maraschino liqueur and lime juice. Although these two drinks have few ingredients in common, the unique combination of citrus, botanical liqueurs and liquor to create a unique sweet and strong cocktail are the same. The two drinks are cousins and happen to be two of my personal favorite cocktails. Try both and see which recipe you love most.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-history\"\u003eHistory \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe share cocktails all the time here on the blog and I’ve honestly never seen such a recent instant classic! Most popular drinks have been around more than 100 years, or close to it! This drink was created by bartender Sam Ross in 2008. Sam is a well known bartender and the co-owner of Attaboy and Diamond Reef in New York City. Although Ross is a NYC bartender, he created this recipe specifically for The Violet Hour in Chicago. He named the drink after the M.I.A. song “Paper Planes,” which he says he was listening to constantly at the time. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eOn creating the recipe, Ross recalls, “That .75-ounce of bourbon, to be sure, I tried it with every type of spirit — rye, applejack, brandy — to really make sure that bourbon was the right fit. And it was.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/paper-plane-cocktail/?tp_image_id=121680\" data-pin-title=\"paper plane cocktail\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-500x500.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%201200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-Cocktail.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-tips-for-making\"\u003eTips for Making \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIf you don’t have Aperol on hand, you can substitute in Campari, but the resulting cocktail will be more bitter (add a bit of simple syrup, to taste, to counteract this). \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eAmaron Nonino is a bit pricey (around $50 per bottle) and can be tricky to find. Some substitutions are Amaro Averna, Amaro Montenegro or Cynar (which is Italian Amaro). \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eGarnish ideas: A tiny paper plane is the most adorable garnish. Other ideas are a lemon peel or orange twist.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-serving-suggestions\"\u003eServing Suggestions \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAppetizers\u003c/strong\u003e – \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/easy-finger-food-ideas/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003e30+ Finger Food Recipes\u003c/a\u003e \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMeal Ideas\u003c/strong\u003e – \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/easy-dinner-recipes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003e60+ Dinner Recipe Ideas\u003c/a\u003e \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMore Cocktails\u003c/strong\u003e – \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/20-delicious-cocktails/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003e50+ Fun Cocktails to Make At Home\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNonalcoholic Drinks\u003c/strong\u003e – \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/roy-rogers-drink/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer no