4738434966\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhat is in a Paper Plane cocktail? \u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eEqual parts bourbon, Aperol, Amaro Nonino and lemon juice. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1704738500716\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eIs Paper Plane a strong cocktail? \u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eYes, the Paper Plane is a spirit forward cocktail. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1733789240546\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eIs the Paper Plane cocktail made with Aperol or Campari? \u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eThe Paper Plane is made with Aperol. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"960\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/paper-plane-cocktail/?tp_image_id=121684\" data-pin-title=\"paper plane cocktail\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane-.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane--300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane--1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane--768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane--100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane--75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane--750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane--730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane--700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane--550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Paper-Plane--156x125.jpg 156w\"